Class Ui

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.Ui
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdminUi, LoginUi, StudentUi
    public class Ui
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for all Ui classes. Contains all the basic methods relevant for input/output to the user.
